Name: _  GADS Web Pages Monitor
Description: Check to see if each GADS web page is up (status 200).  Email test results.

Name: Ping GIS Servers
Description: Troubleshooting for GADS web apps. Look for DNS or server issues, and email results.

Name: Parcel Update
Description: Weekly (Saturday) update of parcels and assessor tables. Email results.

Name: Tacoma Land Use Permits
Description: Download and update json file from CivicData used in Land Use Permits App (https://wspdsmap.cityoftacoma.org/website/PDS/LandUse). Email results.

Name: Tacoma Permit Dashboard
Description: Download and update json file from CivicData used in Tacoma Dashboard App (https://wspdsmap.cityoftacoma.org/website/PDS/PermitDashboard/). Email results.  CivicData table updated daily @ 1:00 am.
Notes: Uses ArcPro credentials to update AGOL data.  Must run from the users machine where ArcPro and AGOL ownership is the same.

Name: Tacoma Permits
Description: Download and update json file from CivicData used in Tacoma Permits App (https://wspdsmap.cityoftacoma.org/website/PDS/Permits). Email results.  CivicData table updated daily @ 1:00 am.

Name: RPZ Vote Data Backup
Description: Backup AGOL data used for RPZ Vote application: https://wspdsmap.cityoftacoma.org/website/PW/Vote_RPZ/
Notes: Uses ArcPro credentials to update AGOL data.  Must run from the users machine where ArcPro and AGOL ownership is the same. | Creates local zipped file of AGOL data.   Also makes a AGOL backup copy named Data_ExportYYYYMMDD_XXXXXX

Name: RPZ Vote Data Update Check
Description: Send Email if RPZ Vote Data has changed on AGOL.
